Package KI304.Stefaniv.Lab2

Class Footwear

java.lang.Object
KI304.Stefaniv.Lab2.Footwear
public class Footwear extends Object
The `Footwear` class represents shoes with various properties such as brand, model, size, sole, laces, upper material, and lace status. It provides methods for getting and setting these properties, lacing and unlacing the footwear, and overridden methods for comparison, hash code, and string representation.
